            p You've seen both. Simply put, the question is ill-formed. No single correct answer! We need the framework:
            ul
              li What: #[strong #[span.fragment tabular data]].
              li Idiom: #[strong #[span.fragment bar or pie chart]].
              ul.fragment
                li.framgment How (encode bar chart): line marks, value channel aligned vertical position, key attribute horizontal position.
                li.framgment How (encode bar chart): area marks (wedges), value channel angle.
              li.fragment #[strong Why]: Identify one, the largest group.
              li.fragment #[strong Why]: Identify one, the 2nd/3rd/4th largest group (rank them).
              li.fragment #[strong Why]: Compare value.
              li.fragment #[strong Why]: Identify distribution of parts of the whole, is a group 1/2, 1/3, 1/4 of whole?.

